Communication:
Blocking:
-MPI_Send - synchronous, blocking send
-MPI_Bsend (as above, but programmer has to allocate buffer)
-MPI_Recv - synchronous, blocking receive
Non-blocking:
-MPI_Isend - "immediate" send
-MPI_Irecv - "immediate" receive
    -extra parameter used, a "request"
    
Check for a message:
-MPI_Probe
-MPI_Iprobe